00:12:07.540 --> 00:12:10.660
it should cause us to rejoice.

00:12:10.660 --> 00:12:13.400
Because we're acknowledging, we're meditating upon,

00:12:13.400 --> 00:12:15.540
we're remembering, we're rehearsing those things

00:12:15.540 --> 00:12:18.500
in our mind, and he says, thou hast smitten

00:12:18.500 --> 00:12:20.980
all mine enemies upon the cheekbone.

